name: Sugar♥Kill  Surprise Treasure Trinket!
description:
Love Sugar♥Kill products but don't know what to get? or maybe feeling lucky?

Perfect for a gift! or just right pack to treat yourself ♥

In this pack, you may receive random assortment and selections of necklace, rings, earrings, studs, brooches, cardigan clip, hair bow, hair slides, hair clips and more!

You will get over $30 worth of stuff!!! 

You can pick a theme or leave it completely random!
(e.g if you pick Kawaii Animal pack, then you will receive more than $30 worth of accessories with animal theme, like owl rings, bunny bow . . . .  etc)

♥ Completely random assortment - mixture of all things from SSKT
♥ Kawaii Animal - assortment of items with animals
♥ Punk Rock baby! - skulls, and punk rock theme item with edge
♥ Sweet Lolita - adorable little items with lolita theme, cupcakes, sweets, lollipops and everything sweet!
